In the diagram, triangles $ABC$ and $CBD$ are isosceles. The perimeter of $\triangle CBD$ is $19,$ the perimeter of $\triangle ABC$ is $20,$ and the length of $BD$ is $7.$ What is the length of $AB?$ [asy]

